                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d754">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">McCormick</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-01-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 21, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. McCormick states that the respective dossiers from Vladivostok, upon which
                    the decisions rendered by the admiralty court are based, can furnish the
                    Department with any detailed information. Asks whether he is to procure and
                    forward translations.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
